Package: FunQ
Title: Functional Quantile methodologies
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Álvaro", "Méndez-Civieta", , "am5490@cumc.columbia.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2044-4170"))
Description: A set of methodologies designed to work with functional data from a 
  quantile perspective. Right now the package implements functions for the estimation 
  of functional quantile principal component analysis (FQPCA). 
  There is work in progress to include functions regarding functional regression.
License: GPL (>= 3) + file LICENSE
